		<arrangement>
			<head>SERIES LIST</head>
			<p>
				<emph render="bold">
					<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s1">Series I.
						Correspondence</ref>
				</emph>Box 1 Correspondence between Wolfson and Perkins and also with
				various research institutes. </p>
			<p>
				<emph render="bold">
					<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s2">Series II. Drafts</ref>
				</emph>Boxes 2-5 Work copies of various chapters </p>
			<p>
				<emph render="bold">
					<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s3">Series III. Notes</ref>
				</emph>Boxes 5-12 Mostly handwritten by co-author A.J. Perkins, from many
				sources. Most of these are copied word for word from Fanny Wright letters although
				some are excerpts of letters. In chronological order except for the first 3 folders
				of notes from newspapers. </p>
			<p>
				<emph render="bold">
					<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s4">Series IV. Wright
						Documents</ref>
				</emph>Box 13-14 Various speeches and lectures by Fanny Wright. These have been microfilmed
				(Film #5216) and should be used rather than originals due to their deteriorating condition.
			</p>
			<p>
				<emph render="bold">
					<ref actuate="onrequest" show="replace" target="s5">Series V. Microfilm</ref>
				</emph>Box 15
			</p>
		</arrangement>
